&gt;  No, not a lie. I did not insist he bring the boxes back after our last falling out. Although I did suggest he should return them, as I just did again. However, he still insists he&#39;s testing them. So why does charge $500 and hour for a test? I don&#39;t care what he does with the boxes, until he tells me my use of the box is wrong! When he says I only get demons, or implies that, then I get pissed. I believe I am in the &quot;other users&quot; group. No onje has a right to take what I made, and claim to be the only authority on it. 
