 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .   Hi Frank & All,  Thanks for clarifying this, as since Chris says on his site that he&#39;s been allowed to KEEP the box(es), I guess, for &quot;testing&quot;! I agree with how you feel about your machine, &quot;Frank&#39;s Box&quot; and YOU are the True Authority on it, NOT some Entertainer/Paranormal Investigator (making people pay a high price to participate!). Well, when we all can do our own Paranormal Investigating or testing & SHARE it with others, he will loose out (It&#39;s Karma). I don&#39;t buy the Chris-tianized ideas/beliefs he&#39;s appearently promoting about the &quot;dangerous&quot; entities/demons or Portals opening up - this is NOT a Ouija Board!!!!! One really doesn&#39;t need an &quot;interpriter&quot; to hear the EVP&#39;s/voices! He&#39;s acting like a bad Medium, I feel. Plus, putting all of us &quot;others&quot; down in our researching/testing . . . like inexperienced researchers = ugh!!! If it wasn&#39;t for YOU, we all, including HIM, wouldn&#39;t be here! I&#39;m sorry, to find out How he&#39;s conducting himself, now.  =Judy=
